                     <lb n="4"/>ma<unclear reason="eccentric_ductus">ṅ</unclear>aḍəg· ḍi kuta kava<lb n="5" break="no"/>li nu mahayu na kaḍatuAn·
                     <lb n="6"/>suravisesa nu marigi sa<lb n="7" break="no"/>kulili<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied> ḍayəḥ nu najur sakala<lb 
